summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 221E, page 8, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Block 6, Seattle Suburban Home Tracts from RM 800 to CG contingent upon the recording of a properly executed, delivered and accepted Property Use and Development Agreement pertaining to such property. (Petition of Michael W. Vergillo, C.F. 282712)
